quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  38,1,"Saad. Mi woo…óndirii Alqur'aana, jom waa."
  38,2,"Si ko woni, yeddu…ďe …ďe ngonii e townitaare e lurral !"
  38,3,"∆äuu…óii e gire …óen Min kalki, ado ma…ď…ďe, …ďe noddi faabo, kono tawi ko bonatno bonii."
  38,4,"∆Āe Ňčal…ói, nde jeertinoowo jiyaa…óo e ma…ď…ďe, arata …ďe. Yeddu…ďe …ďen mbi'i: "Oo, ko bileejo keewu…óo fenaande,"
  38,5,"Kere o wa…óay dewetee…ói …óin, dewetee…óo gooto? Pellet, …óum ko hu'unde haawniinde non"."
  38,6,"Mbatu ma…ď…ďe ngun huccitiri wiide: "Yehee, tabiton e dewetee…ói mon …óin. ∆äuum …óoo, ko hu'unde e…ď…ďanaande."
  38,7,"Min nanaali fii …óum, e diina sakkitiika kan. ∆äum wonaani, si wonaa ko fefkindaa."
  38,8,"Kere ko e makko JaŇčtoore nden jippotoo hakkunde amen?" Si ko woni, …ďe ngonii e cikkitagol Jantoore am nden. Wurin, ko fii …ďe mee…óaali taho, lepte am …óen!"
  38,9,"Kaa …ďe njogiti ngaluuji yurmeende Joomi maa, poolu…óo, Dokko O?"
  38,10,"Kaa ko kam…ďe woodani laamagol kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde majji? Haray yo …ďe ∆īeenŇču …ďe ∆īawa!"
  38,11,"Ko …ďe konu hoyngu no, foolet e 'pe…óle …óen!"
  38,12,"Ado ma…ď…ďe, yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďen njedduno, e Aadi'en e Fir'awna jom-peme,"
  38,13,"e Samuuda'en, e yim…ďe Luutu …ďe, e yim…ďe pitaaji …ďen; ko …ďeen ngoni fedde (fennu…ďe) …ďeen."
  38,14,"Kala …ďee wonaani, si wonaa o njeddi ii Nulaa…ďe …ďen. Lepte Am …óen jojji e ma…ď…ďe!"
  38,15,"∆Āee cabbaaki, si wonaa ha'acaango gooto, ngo alaa ruttorde."
  38,16,"∆Āe mbii': "Joomi amen, yaccinan min ge…óal lepte amen, ado √Ďalaande hasboore nden"."